"""
X Article → PDF Web App
=======================
Lightweight web server that converts X articles to styled PDFs.
All images are embedded as base64 for reliable rendering.
PDFs are saved to disk so they survive a failed download.

Access from any device on your network:
    http://<your-ip>:8765/

Usage:
    x-article-web              # runs on http://0.0.0.0:8765
    x-article-web --port 9000  # custom port
"""

